burlap.oomdp.statehashing

Class ImmutableStateHashableStateFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.SimpleHashableStateFactory
      • burlap.oomdp.statehashing.ImmutableStateHashableStateFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HashableStateFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FixedSizeStateHashableStateFactory

    public class ImmutableStateHashableStateFactory
extends SimpleHashableStateFactory
    This Hashing factory works for states that implement the ImmutableStateInterface. It caches the value by default, and also will check object equality through the == comparison, since ImmutableStates may share the same objects.
    Author:
    brawner
